def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('a', 'Wa')

print(insert_before_character('banana'))  # bWanWanWa
print(insert_before_character('apple'))  # Wapple
print(insert_before_character('water'))  # Wwater
print(insert_before_character('orange'))  # orange
